  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "uv8pYwFh4jUdjWhyLaj/SNjbjwE0JHJC7bImlCqSWD8=",
    "originContent": "| Input                | Description                                                                                     | Required | Default     |",
    "translatedContent": "| 入力                 | 説明                                                                                         | 必須     | デフォルト   |"
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "8+Pq0Yq6rBGyliQhzDgS2Yo1RJjG4A/RNPCOaMZrA0E=",
    "originContent": "| -------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- | ----------- |",
    "translatedContent": "| -------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- | ----------- |"
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "QwZO3+zeiRN1FM16dhM9unIrYarI0yiwVOcSv+aUWAk=",
    "originContent": "| `tailscale_authkey`  | Tailscale OAuth client secret or Auth Key.                                                      | **Yes**  | N/A         |",
    "translatedContent": "| `tailscale_authkey`  | Tailscale OAuth クライアントシークレットまたは認証キー。                                     | **必須** | N/A         |"
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "+cekAwWKUzrPweGqnZYbKZgiLh2JfqWz8maDiUofV+o=",
    "originContent": "| `tailscale_hostname` | Hostname to register with Tailscale.                                                            | **Yes**  | N/A         |",
    "translatedContent": "| `tailscale_hostname` | Tailscale に登録するホスト名。                                                               | **必須** | N/A         |"
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "KI3MoAQDN4VViwXqtVLVbu0QAl2AzXlo5z2XaTM1t8Y=",
    "originContent": "| `tailscale_tags`     | Tags to advertise to Tailscale (e.g. `tag:nix-ci-builder`).                                     | **Yes**  | N/A         |",
    "translatedContent": "| `tailscale_tags`     | Tailscale に広告するタグ（例：`tag:nix-ci-builder`）。                                      | **必須** | N/A         |"
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "knWQDP6lPESY+QzlzHAQEUw79+oxJhZi9Xl6Vq5/zxk=",
    "originContent": "| `role`               | Role of the current job: `\"builder\"` or `\"coordinator\"`.                                        | Yes      | `\"builder\"` |",
    "translatedContent": "| `role`               | 現在のジョブの役割：`\"builder\"` または `\"coordinator\"`。                                    | 必須     | `\"builder\"` |"
  },
  {
    "row": 99,
    "rowsha": "dxLYq4h0jBE+J2z+2hOK8k9D75SJ0jsMt+RhGpw8WS0=",
    "originContent": "| `builders`           | Space separated list of full builder hostnames to wait for. (_Required if role is coordinator_) | No       | `\"\"`        |",
    "translatedContent": "| `builders`           | 待機する完全なビルダーホスト名の空白区切りリスト。（役割が coordinator の場合必須）          | いいえ   | `\"\"`        |"
  },
  {
    "row": 100,
    "rowsha": "iIrB9dsoPdBFNmot+aZ71FUhDS00M/ZOAT8bSmnoP5c=",
    "originContent": "| `builder_timeout`    | Maximum time (in seconds) the builder should wait before self-terminating.                      | No       | `\"300\"`     |",
    "translatedContent": "| `builder_timeout`    | ビルダーが自己終了するまでの最大待機時間（秒）。                                            | いいえ   | `\"300\"`     |"
  },
  {
    "row": 101,
    "rowsha": "DC8W3x80dU3dgjz4ctSh9fBKuO07oyZVjKg+QD3ZKiA=",
    "originContent": "| `extra_nix_config`   | Extra Nix configuration to append to `/etc/nix/nix.conf`.                                       | No       | `\"\"`        |",
    "translatedContent": "| `extra_nix_config`   | `/etc/nix/nix.conf` に追記する追加の Nix 設定。                                            | いいえ   | `\"\"`        |"
  },
  {
    "row": 102,
