    "originContent": "## Usage",
    "translatedContent": "## 使用法"
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "92xhw5mFxrR4vO4r/oq+riyuyHMu68doMkZUTMg0Dqg=",
    "originContent": "### Full Distributed Build Example",
    "translatedContent": "### 完全分散ビルドの例"
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "/oQxugUOiU1Zp3UlaS3ib5uO9WAoBsoMrRDGUg7WFuo=",
    "originContent": "Below is a complete workflow (`nix-build.yml`) that dynamically spins up multiple runner architectures (Ubuntu x86, Ubuntu ARM, macOS x86, macOS Apple Silicon), connects them together, and runs a distributed Nix build.",
    "translatedContent": "以下は複数のランナーアーキテクチャ（Ubuntu x86、Ubuntu ARM、macOS x86、macOS Apple Silicon）を動的に起動し、それらを接続して分散 Nix ビルドを実行する完全なワークフロー (`nix-build.yml`) です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "vXMN4L2J76dgThR86xX1987FbMCm97PUavE5OkyCBx0=",
    "originContent": "If you are building a heavy NixOS configuration and simply want to speed it up using horizontal scaling, you can change the `BUILDER_COUNTS` to spawn multiple identical x86 runners. For example:",
    "translatedContent": "重い NixOS 構成をビルドしていて、単に水平スケーリングで速度を上げたい場合は、`BUILDER_COUNTS` を変更して複数の同一 x86 ランナーを起動することができます。例えば："
  },
  {
    "row": 110,
    "rowsha": "GHSFbbd15YiLhMSlPa7GcyERbk7OKNNZ5hFsX2DaBwQ=",
    "originContent": "`BUILDER_COUNTS: '{\"ubuntu-24.04\": 4}'` ",
    "translatedContent": "`BUILDER_COUNTS: '{\"ubuntu-24.04\": 4}'`  "
  },
  {
    "row": 111,
    "rowsha": "bYS3hvn7JyX1zo2PJn4VDSI1adyeZYoWU5m5g+4Zkus=",
    "originContent": "This will instantly give you a build farm with 16 CPU cores (4 runners × 4 cores) to process derivations in parallel.",
    "translatedContent": "これにより、16 CPU コア（4 ランナー × 4 コア）のビルドファームが即座に得られ、派生物を並列処理できます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 112,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 113,
    "rowsha": "Q1DI2M2GyATgRj77Cv7s/LYTmoeAeygy1x/DqF/kjRI=",
    "originContent": "Since GitHub Hosted Runners are ephemeral, all build artifacts in the Nix store will be lost when the workflow finishes. To reap the benefits of your distributed builds in future CI runs or on your local machines, it is highly recommended to push the results to a binary cache like [Cachix](https://www.cachix.org) or [Attic](https://github.com/zhaofengli/attic).",
    "translatedContent": "GitHub ホステッドランナーは一時的なため、ワークフロー完了時に Nix ストア内のすべてのビルド成果物は失われます。将来の CI 実行やローカルマシンで分散ビルドの利点を享受するためには、成果物を [Cachix](https://www.cachix.org) や [Attic](https://github.com/zhaofengli/attic) のようなバイナリキャッシュにプッシュすることを強く推奨します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
